举例子，我之前在理想和现实的撕裂中难以抉择，直到后来才采取了折中的方式。原因是什么？原因就是我看到了这两条路的困境，理想主义者他们往往在追求理同时导致现实一塌糊涂，最终怀揣着理想抱憾而终，而现实主义者他们往往在追求了些许的现实后，他们的灵魂日益孤独，最终也是怀揣着带不走的现实抱憾而终。 这两条路都是如此，所以我才会畏首畏尾，正是因为看的过于透彻，所以才会畏首畏尾，没了热血和激情。 所以我们在“怀疑”的过程中彷徨，在彷徨的过程中“痛苦”，接着导致了各种各样的心理问题，而后便是走向“不彻底的虚无”，我们想建设，想获得现实，但又太追求理想，太追求内心的完美，所以我们既想建设又想放弃，这便是一种恶性循环。"},"attached_info":"CkAI6P311da32atcEAMaCTEwNzgyMTM2NSDer9exBjAAONwBQCtyCTY1NDk0NjU1N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-1b4eee6207387596b3610962db8a3167_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"44_1715009024.37054","card_id":"Q_27522719","target":{"id":27522719,"title":"最好的Python入门教材是哪本？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/27522719","type":"question","created":1420940889,"answer_count":222,"follower_count":3468,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[872,37027],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"目前接触过两本，一本是Hetland的Python基础教程，一本是Python for kids。"},"attached_info":"Cj0I6P311da32atcEAMaBzMxOTE4OTcg2azHpQUwADiMG0AscggyNzUyMjcxOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e05a0877ec050ab59d7c88bac303411b_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"45_1715009024.37319","card_id":"Q_653795784","target":{"id":653795784,"title":"去健身房运动与在家运动有何区别？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653795784","type":"question","created":1713822315,"answer_count":85,"follower_count":117,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[658,833,972,3360343,3403277],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I6P311da32atcEAMaCTEwNzU2NTU2OCDrtJuxBjA